<p>These Marry Me Chickpeas &#8211; the vegetarian equivalent of Marry Me Chicken &#8211; are about to have you head over heels for chickpeas! Wrapped in a creamy Tuscan sauce and absolutely loaded with flavor, they&#8217;ve quickly become one of my favorite <a href="https://www.liveeatlearn.com/canned-chickpea-recipes/">ways to use a can of chickpeas</a>! They&#8217;re:</p>



<ol>
<li><strong>Easy to make</strong>, requiring just 1 pan and 15 minutes</li>



<li><strong>Served any way</strong>, like with a thick slice of sourdough bread or over a bed of rice</li>



<li><strong>Made with mostly pantry staples</strong> so you can enjoy this without much advanced planning!</li>
</ol>


