<h2 class="wp-block-heading" id="h-how-to-make-marry-me-chickpeas">How to make Marry Me Chickpeas</h2>


<p>Making this dish takes just 1 pan and less than 15 minutes. You&#8217;ll just:</p>



<ol>
<li><strong>Make the flavor base</strong>, a delicious combination of butter, garlic, and spices.</li>



<li><strong>Add the fillings</strong> and cook for a few minutes.</li>



<li><strong>Finish</strong> it off with cream, parmesan, and basil!</li>
</ol>



